Body:
@kclass
class Other:
    an: AN(10)
    n: N(5)
@kclass
class Something:
    a: N(10)
    b: AN(20)
    other: Other
    others: List[Other]
    c: N(5)
    d: AN(10)
sth = Something(1, 2, Other(3, 4), [Other(1, 1), Other(1, 1)], 5, 6)
assert sth.bytes == b'NANANNANNANNNAN'
patch('kformat.kproperty.AN.to_bytes', lambda s, v: b'AN')patch('kformat.kproperty.N.to_bytes', lambda s, v: b'N')
